<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Biosphere – Stakeholder Analysis</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0a0f1e;
    --surface: #101827;
    --surface2: #1a2540;
    --accent1: #00e5c0;
    --accent2: #5b8fff;
    --accent3: #ff6b6b;
    --accent4: #ffc94a;
    --accent5: #b57bff;
    --text: #e8edf8;
    --muted: #7a8aaa;
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ---- HERO ---- */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 64px 48px 56px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 60% 0%, rgba(0,229,192,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 90% 100%, rgba(91,143,255,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,192,0.3);
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 54px);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .hero h1 span { color: var(--accent1); }
  .hero p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent1);
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* ---- SECTION TITLES ---- */
  .section {
    padding: 56px 48px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .section-num {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  /* ---- POWER-INTEREST MAP ---- */
  .map-wrap {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    max-height: 420px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .map-axis-x, .map-axis-y {
    position: absolute;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  .map-axis-x { left: 50%; top: 0; width: 1px; height: 100%; }
  .map-axis-y { top: 50%; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 1px; }
  .map-label {
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .map-label.bottom { bottom: 12px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); }
  .map-label.top { top: 12px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); }
  .map-label.left { left: 12px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(-90deg); }
  .map-label.right { right: 12px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(90deg); }

  .quad-label {
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    opacity: 0.35;
  }
  .quad-label.tl { top: 16px; left: 16px; }
  .quad-label.tr { top: 16px; right: 16px; text-align: right; }
  .quad-label.bl { bottom: 30px; left: 16px; }
  .quad-label.br { bottom: 30px; right: 16px; text-align: right; }

  .node {
    position: absolute;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    cursor: default;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .node-dot {
    width: 14px; height: 14px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--bg);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px currentColor;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .node-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    white-space: nowrap;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  /* ---- STAKEHOLDER CARDS ---- */
  .cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
    background: var(--card-accent, var(--accent1));
  }
  .card-icon {
    font-size: 26px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: var(--card-accent, var(--accent1));
  }
  .card-sub {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .card-section-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    margin-top: 14px;
  }
  .card-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .card-list li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #bec9e0;
    padding-left: 14px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .card-list li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--card-accent, var(--accent1));
    font-size: 11px;
    top: 1px;
  }
  .card-highlight {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--card-accent, var(--accent1));
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: 14px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--card-accent, var(--accent1));
  }

  /* PAIN LEVEL BAR */
  .pain-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 14px;
  }
  .pain-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); min-width: 70px; }
  .pain-track {
    flex: 1;
    height: 5px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border-radius: 100px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .pain-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 100px;
    background: var(--card-accent, var(--accent1));
    width: var(--fill);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
  .pain-val { font-size: 11px; font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; color: var(--card-accent); min-width: 28px; text-align: right; }

  /* BADGE */
  .badge-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-top: 12px; }
  .badge {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* ---- STRATEGY TABLE ---- */
  .strategy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .strategy-cell {
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .strategy-cell.header {
    background: var(--surface2);
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .strategy-cell .sh-name {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .strategy-cell p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #8a9bb8;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ---- HYPOTHESIS SECTION ---- */
  .hyp-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .hyp-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 22px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .hyp-num {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .hyp-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--accent2);
  }
  .hyp-body { font-size: 13px; color: #8a9bb8; line-height: 1.55; }
  .hyp-validate {
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent1);
    padding-left: 12px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent1);
  }

  /* ---- FOOTER ---- */
  footer {
    padding: 32px 48px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  footer span { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); }

  /* ---- RESPONSIVE ---- */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero, .section { padding: 40px 24px; }
    .strategy-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    footer { padding: 24px; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .strategy-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-stats { gap: 20px; }
  }

  /* Subtle grid bg */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.013) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.013) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 48px 48px;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  main { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<main>

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-tag">Biosphere · Customer Discovery</div>
  <h1>Stakeholder <span>Mapping</span><br>& Research Report</h1>
  <p>A thorough analysis of who Biosphere serves, why we chose them, and how their pain shapes our product decisions.</p>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">4</span><span class="stat-label">Stakeholder Groups</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">$30K</span><span class="stat-label">Avg. FTO Search Cost</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">$500/hr</span><span class="stat-label">IP Attorney Rate</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">~6 wks</span><span class="stat-label">Avg. Legal Review Wait</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ===== SECTION 1 – POWER-INTEREST MAP ===== -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">01</span>
    <span class="section-title">Power vs. Interest Map</span>
  </div>

  <div class="map-wrap">
    <div class="map-axis-x"></div>
    <div class="map-axis-y"></div>

    <span class="map-label bottom">LOW INTEREST → HIGH INTEREST</span>
    <span class="map-label left">LOW POWER ↑ HIGH POWER</span>
    <span class="quad-label tl" style="color:#ffc94a">KEEP SATISFIED</span>
    <span class="quad-label tr" style="color:#00e5c0">MANAGE CLOSELY</span>
    <span class="quad-label bl" style="color:#7a8aaa">MONITOR</span>
    <span class="quad-label br" style="color:#5b8fff">KEEP INFORMED</span>

    <!-- Biotech Startups – high interest, high power = top-right -->
    <div class="node" style="left:74%;top:28%;color:var(--accent1)">
      <div class="node-dot" style="background:var(--accent1);width:18px;height:18px;"></div>
      <div class="node-label" style="color:var(--accent1)">Biotech Startups</div>
    </div>
    <!-- Pharma R&D – high interest, high power -->
    <div class="node" style="left:83%;top:18%;color:var(--accent4)">
      <div class="node-dot" style="background:var(--accent4);width:16px;height:16px;"></div>
      <div class="node-label" style="color:var(--accent4)">Pharma R&D</div>
    </div>
    <!-- Academic Researchers – high interest, medium power = right/mid -->
    <div class="node" style="left:72%;top:60%;color:var(--accent2)">
      <div class="node-dot" style="background:var(--accent2);width:15px;height:15px;"></div>
      <div class="node-label" style="color:var(--accent2)">Academic Researchers</div>
    </div>
    <!-- Regulatory Bodies – low interest, high power = top-left -->
    <div class="node" style="left:22%;top:22%;color:var(--accent3)">
      <div class="node-dot" style="background:var(--accent3);width:14px;height:14px;"></div>
      <div class="node-label" style="color:var(--accent3)">Regulators / Patent Offices</div>
    </div>
    <!-- IP Law Firms – medium interest, medium power = mid -->
    <div class="node" style="left:55%;top:50%;color:var(--accent5)">
      <div class="node-dot" style="background:var(--accent5);width:13px;height:13px;"></div>
      <div class="node-label" style="color:var(--accent5)">IP Law Firms</div>
    </div>
    <!-- University Tech Transfer – low/mid interest, mid power -->
    <div class="node" style="left:36%;top:62%;color:var(--muted)">
      <div class="node-dot" style="background:var(--muted);width:11px;height:11px;"></div>
      <div class="node-label">University TTO</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:14px;">Bubble size reflects relative relevance to Biosphere's core value proposition. Nodes in the top-right quadrant are primary targets.</p>
</div>

<!-- ===== SECTION 2 – STAKEHOLDER CARDS ===== -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">02</span>
    <span class="section-title">Stakeholder Deep-Dives</span>
  </div>

  <div class="cards-grid">

    <!-- CARD 1: Biotech Startups -->
    <div class="card" style="--card-accent: var(--accent1)">
      <div class="card-icon">🧬</div>
      <div class="card-title">Biotech Startups</div>
      <div class="card-sub">EARLY-STAGE · SEED TO SERIES B · PRIMARY USER</div>

      <div class="card-section-label">Who They Are</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#bec9e0;">Small teams (5–50 people) building genomic tools, diagnostics, or therapeutics. Often founded by researchers transitioning from academia. Working with novel or modified DNA sequences daily.</p>

      <div class="card-section-label">Core Pain Points</div>
      <ul class="card-list">
        <li>Cannot afford $10K–$30K freedom-to-operate searches at seed stage</li>
        <li>Patent landscape in synthetic biology is dense and overlapping — CRISPR battles alone cost $10M+</li>
        <li>Legal uncertainty blocks investor confidence and funding rounds</li>
        <li>No technical staff with legal expertise; scientists ≠ IP lawyers</li>
        <li>Undetected infringement risk can sink a company post-launch</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="pain-row">
        <span class="pain-label">Financial Risk</span>
        <div class="pain-track"><div class="pain-fill" style="--fill:92%"></div></div>
        <span class="pain-val">9.2</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-row">
        <span class="pain-label">Urgency</span>
        <div class="pain-track"><div class="pain-fill" style="--fill:88%"></div></div>
        <span class="pain-val">8.8</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-row">
        <span class="pain-label">Tech Readiness</span>
        <div class="pain-track"><div class="pain-fill" style="--fill:80%"></div></div>
        <span class="pain-val">8.0</span>
      </div>

      <div class="card-section-label">What They Need From Biosphere</div>
      <ul class="card-list">
        <li>Fast, affordable pre-screening before committing R&D budget</li>
        <li>Traffic-light risk score they can show investors</li>
        <li>No legal expertise required to interpret results</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="card-highlight">💡 Willingness to Pay: $50–$200/month (SaaS). Investors actively pressure this group to show IP clearance.</div>

      <div class="badge-row">
        <span class="badge">Primary Buyer</span>
        <span class="badge">High Urgency</span>
        <span class="badge">Investor-Driven</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CARD 2: Academic Researchers -->
    <div class="card" style="--card-accent: var(--accent2)">
      <div class="card-icon">🎓</div>
      <div class="card-title">Academic Researchers</div>
      <div class="card-sub">PHD STUDENTS · POST-DOCS · PRINCIPAL INVESTIGATORS · SECONDARY USER</div>

      <div class="card-section-label">Who They Are</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#bec9e0;">University-based scientists working on genomics, molecular biology, or bioinformatics. Often university-funded (non-commercial), but increasingly tied to commercial grants or spinoffs. Use BLAST and FASTA tools daily.</p>

      <div class="card-section-label">Core Pain Points</div>
      <ul class="card-list">
        <li>Assume academic use is automatically exempt — often wrong when tied to commercial grants</li>
        <li>Myriad Genetics precedent: researchers received cease-and-desist letters for BRCA1/BRCA2 work</li>
        <li>No awareness of biopiracy regulations (Nagoya Protocol, CBD treaties)</li>
        <li>Publishing patented sequences can create compliance liability</li>
        <li>Tech transfer offices (TTOs) are slow and bureaucratic — weeks of delays</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="pain-row">
        <span class="pain-label">Financial Risk</span>
        <div class="pain-track"><div class="pain-fill" style="--fill:55%"></div></div>
        <span class="pain-val">5.5</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-row">
        <span class="pain-label">Urgency</span>
        <div class="pain-track"><div class="pain-fill" style="--fill:60%"></div></div>
        <span class="pain-val">6.0</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-row">
        <span class="pain-label">Tech Readiness</span>
        <div class="pain-track"><div class="pain-fill" style="--fill:90%"></div></div>
        <span class="pain-val">9.0</span>
      </div>

      <div class="card-section-label">What They Need From Biosphere</div>
      <ul class="card-list">
        <li>Pre-publication sequence clearance check</li>
        <li>Compliance guidance for biodiversity treaties by jurisdiction</li>
        <li>Institutional/group subscription (PI buys for whole lab)</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="card-highlight">💡 Best acquisition channel: university partnerships & lab software tools. High FASTA/BLAST familiarity = low onboarding friction.</div>

      <div class="badge-row">
        <span class="badge">High Volume</span>
        <span class="badge">Low Awareness</span>
        <span class="badge">Institutional Buy</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CARD 3: Pharma R&D Teams -->
    <div class="card" style="--card-accent: var(--accent4)">
      <div class="card-icon">💊</div>
      <div class="card-title">Pharma R&D Teams</div>
      <div class="card-sub">MID-TO-LARGE PHARMA · R&D COMPLIANCE · SECONDARY BUYER</div>

      <div class="card-section-label">Who They Are</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#bec9e0;">Internal research divisions at mid-to-large pharmaceutical companies working on therapeutic proteins, gene therapies, biosimilars. Must navigate dense patent thickets before entering clinical trials.</p>

      <div class="card-section-label">Core Pain Points</div>
      <ul class="card-list">
        <li>Established companies spend $100K+ on FTO analysis per product launch</li>
        <li>Overlapping patent claims in personalized medicine and synthetic biology are frequent</li>
        <li>Internal IP teams are expensive and bottlenecked — delay research timelines</li>
        <li>Need multi-jurisdiction clearance (US, EU, India) before global trials</li>
        <li>Historical cases (Genentech vs. Sanofi, Amgen patent battles) show stakes are enormous</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="pain-row">
        <span class="pain-label">Financial Risk</span>
        <div class="pain-track"><div class="pain-fill" style="--fill:98%"></div></div>
        <span class="pain-val">9.8</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-row">
        <span class="pain-label">Urgency</span>
        <div class="pain-track"><div class="pain-fill" style="--fill:72%"></div></div>
        <span class="pain-val">7.2</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-row">
        <span class="pain-label">Tech Readiness</span>
        <div class="pain-track"><div class="pain-fill" style="--fill:65%"></div></div>
        <span class="pain-val">6.5</span>
      </div>

      <div class="card-section-label">What They Need From Biosphere</div>
      <ul class="card-list">
        <li>Enterprise-grade API integration into existing R&D pipeline</li>
        <li>Multi-jurisdiction compliance reports</li>
        <li>Audit trail for regulatory submissions and investor due diligence</li>
      </ul>

